  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5522814/" class="title-link">很失望的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5522814"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51693510/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51693510/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">diabloyu</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-07-27"
      class="main-meta">2012-07-27 08:15:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5522814_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作者用东拉西扯的叙述手法，无非在反复强调三点： 1、泊松分布不靠谱， 2、93%有规律+7%爆发， 3、爆发是幂律分布。 对于为何幂律分布，如何爆发， 爆发背后隐藏的原因，则毫无分析。  就这三点，让作者写出一本书来，真佩服。 而且居然还卖60块一本。  烂书一本，非常失望。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5522814/#comments">(25回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">69有用 / 20没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5522814_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5522814_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



